quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Ndayira ekibuga kino (Makkah)
  90,2,Nga naawe (Muhammad) oli mutuuze mu kibuga kino
  90,3,Era ndayira omuzadde ne baazaala
  90,4,Mazima twakola omuntu nga lubeerera abeera mu kutawaana
  90,5,Alowooza nti tewali n’omu ayinza ku musobola
  90,6,Ng’agamba nti nsaasanyiza emmaali nyingi nnyo
  90,7,Alowooza nti tewali n’omu amulaba
  90,8,Tetwamuwa amaaso abiri
  90,9,N’olulimi n’emimwa ebiri
  90,10,Era ne tumulungamya okumanya amakubo abiri (ery'ekirungi n'ery'ekibi)
  90,11,Kale singa yabikozesa mu kuvvuunuka obizibu (bw'olunaku lw'enkomerero n'aba nga akozesa bye yafuna naafunamu e nkomerero)
  90,12,Abaffe obuzibu obumanyi (n'ekiyinza okubukuyambako)
  90,13,Kuta muddu
  90,14,Oba okuliisa mu kiseera eky’enjala
  90,15,"Mulekwa, owooluganda olw’okumpi"
  90,16,Oba omwavu lunkupe
  90,17,Ate era n’abeera mu abo abakkiriza. Ng’era balaamiragana obugumiikiriza nga bwe balaamiragana okusaasiragana
  90,18,Abo nno beebo abokubeera ku mukono ogwa ddyo
  90,19,Naye abo abawakanya e bigambo byaffe baakubeera ku mukono ogwa kkono
  90,20,Bagenda kubeera mu muliro omusaanikire
  91,1,Ndayira e njuba n’okwaka kwayo
  91,2,Era ndayira o mwezi bweguba nga gugoberedde e njuba (ng’egudde)
  91,3,Era ndayira obudde obw’emisana nga bwerudde enjuba
  91,4,Era ndayira ekiro bwe kiba nga kigibisse
  91,5,Era ndayira e ggulu n’eyalitonda
  91,6,Era ndayira e nsi n’oyo eyajaaliira
  91,7,Era ndayira omuntu n’eyamutonda
  91,8,N’amuwa okwawula wakati w’ekibi n’ekirungi
  91,9,Yeesiimye alongoosa omwoyogwe okuguggya mu bibi
  91,10,Aviiriddemu awo oyo agunnyika mu bibi
  91,11,"Abantu ba Thamuud, olw'obwonoonefu bwabwe baalimbisa (omubaka waabwe)"
  91,12,Asinga obwonoonefu mu bo bwe yeesowolayo (naafumita engamiya)
  91,13,Omubaka wa Katonda n’abagamba “muleke e ngamiya ya Katonda n’okunywa kwayo”
  91,14,Kyokka ne bamulimbisa ne bagifumita. Katonda omulabirizi waabwe kwe kubabuutikira olw’obwonoonefu bwabwe awatali n’omu kuwona
  91,15,Era tatya nkomerero y'ekyo (eky'okubazikiriza)
  92,1,Ndayira ekiro bwe kiba kibisse (e nsi)
  92,2,Ndayira n'obudde bwemisana bwe buba nga bwetadde
  92,3,Ndayira oyo eyatonda ekisajja n’ekikazi
  92,4,Mazima ddala okulafuubana kwa mmwe si kwe kumu
  92,5,"N'olwekyo, omuntu awaayo ekintu kyonna ng’atya Katonda"
  92,6,Nakkiriza e birungi. (ebiva mu kukkiriza Katonda)
  92,7,Tujja kumwanguyiza e kkubo erimutuusa eri obwangu
  92,8,Ate oyo akodowala ne yeegaggasa (ng’alowooza nti ebiri ewa Katonda tabyetaaga)
  92,9,N’alimbisa obubaka obwakkira ku Nabbi Muhammad
  92,10,Tujja kumwanguyiza okutuuka eri obuzibu
  92,11,N’obugaggabwe tebugenda kumugasa ng’ayingidde okuzikirira (olw’ebikolwa bye ebibi)
  92,12,Mazima kuli ku ffe okulungamya
  92,13,Era mazima ebikwata ku nkomerero ne nsi biri mu buyinza bwaffe
  92,14,Mbeekesa omuliro ogubumbujja
  92,15,Taliguyingira okugyako oyo omwonoonefu ennyo
  92,16,Oyo alimbisa (e bigambo bya Katonda) n'ayawukana (ku kugondera n'okukkiriza Katonda)
  92,17,"So nga oyo asinga okutya Katonda, ajja kugwesambisibwa"
  92,18,Oyo awaayo ku by'alina ng’anoonya okwetukuza eri Katonda (so si bandabe oba okwatiikirira)
  92,19,Nga tewali n'omu alina kiyinza ku musasulwa
  92,20,Wabula okunoonya okusiimwa ewa mukamaawe owa waggulu ennyo
  92,21,Mazima ddala ajja kusiima (ky’anaasasulwa)
  93,1,Ndayira ekiseera ky’a kalasa mayanzi
  93,2,Era ndayira e kiro bwekiba nga kikutte
  93,3,Omuleziwo Katonda takwabuliranga (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) era takukyawanga
  93,4,Era ddala e nkomerero y’ennungi gy’oli okusinga entandikwa
  93,5,Era ddala Omuleziwo ajja kukuwa naawe osiime
  93,6,Teyakusanga ng’oli mulekwa n'akulabirira
  93,7,Era teyakusanga nga tomanyi n’akulungamya
  93,8,Era teyakusanga nga oli mwavu n’akugaggawaza
  93,9,Kale nno mulekwa tomukaayuukiranga
  93,10,N’omuntu asaba tomuboggoleranga
  93,11,Ate era e kyengera kyonna Omuleziwo Katonda ky’abanga akuwadde kinyumyengako